"title": "5844: emotions",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5844: emotions",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Scripture portrays both human beings and God as having emotions. Human emotions and sentiments are of importance to the life of faith. Human feelings can be positive or negative and are subject to change and misinterpretation.</p>\n<h2>Emotions shown by God</h2>\n<h3>Love</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut7:7-Deut7:8\">DEU 7:7–7:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa43:4\">ISA 43:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer31:3\">JER 31:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos11:1\">HOS 11:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark10:21\">MRK 10:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John13:1\">JHN 13:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John17:23\">JHN 17:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John4:8\">1JN 4:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John4:10\">1JN 4:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John4:19\">1JN 4:19</a></p>\n<h3>Compassion</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps103:13\">PSA 103:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod33:19\">EXO 33:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut13:17\">DEU 13:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg2:18\">JDG 2:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps116:5\">PSA 116:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt9:36\">MAT 9:36</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt14:14\">MAT 14:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt15:32\">MAT 15:32</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark8:2\">MRK 8:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt20:34\">MAT 20:34</a></p>\n<h3>Joy and delight</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer32:41\">JER 32:41</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut30:9\">DEU 30:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa62:4\">ISA 62:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke15:32\">LUK 15:32</a></p>\n<h3>Anger</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod22:24\">EXO 22:24</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut6:14-Deut6:15\">DEU 6:14–6:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh7:1\">JOS 7:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer7:20\">JER 7:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek5:13\">EZK 5:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt21:12-Matt21:13\">MAT 21:12–21:13</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark11:15-Mark11:17\">MRK 11:15–11:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke19:45-Luke19:46\">LUK 19:45–19:46</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John2:14-John2:17\">JHN 2:14–2:17</a></p>\n<h2>Human emotions experienced by God's people</h2>\n<h3>Joy</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa51:11\">ISA 51:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam2:1\">1SA 2:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps4:7\">PSA 4:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps28:7\">PSA 28:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps30:11-Ps30:12\">PSA 30:11–30:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke1:47\">LUK 1:47</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts16:25\">ACT 16:25</a></p>\n<h3>Love for God and one another</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps116:1\">PSA 116:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps18:1\">PSA 18:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John21:17\">JHN 21:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John4:11-1John4:12\">1JN 4:11–4:12</a></p>\n<h3>Sorrow and pain</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps6:6-Ps6:7\">PSA 6:6–6:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam1:7-1Sam1:8\">1SA 1:7–1:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam1:10\">1SA 1:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam18:33\">2SA 18:33</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs19:3-1Kgs19:4\">1KI 19:3–19:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps88:15\">PSA 88:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:28\">PSA 119:28</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps137:1\">PSA 137:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer15:18\">JER 15:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic7:1\">MIC 7:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John11:19\">JHN 11:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John11:31\">JHN 11:31</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John11:33\">JHN 11:33</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom9:2-Rom9:3\">ROM 9:2–9:3</a></p>\n<h3>Fear</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod3:6\">EXO 3:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen18:15\">GEN 18:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh9:24\">JOS 9:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa35:4\">ISA 35:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa41:10\">ISA 41:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt8:26\">MAT 8:26</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark4:40-Mark4:41\">MRK 4:40–4:41</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke8:25\">LUK 8:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt28:8\">MAT 28:8</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark16:8\">MRK 16:8</a></p>\n<h3>God's people are to feel for one another</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil1:7-Phil1:8\">PHP 1:7–1:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod22:21\">EXO 22:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod23:9\">EXO 23:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor12:25-1Cor12:26\">1CO 12:25–12:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor6:11-2Cor6:13\">2CO 6:11–6:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor7:2-2Cor7:3\">2CO 7:2–7:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor11:29\">2CO 11:29</a></p>\n<h2>Believers are to control their emotions</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal5:22-Gal5:23\">GAL 5:22–5:23</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov25:28\">PRO 25:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:26\">EPH 4:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph5:18\">EPH 5:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col3:8\">COL 3:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim2:8\">1TI 2:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas1:19-Jas1:20\">JAS 1:19–1:20</a></p>\n<h2>Emotions are changeable</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov14:13\">PRO 14:13</a></strong></p>\n<h3>The wicked may feel an unwarranted sense of security</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos6:1\">AMO 6:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan8:25\">DAN 8:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan11:21\">DAN 11:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan11:24\">DAN 11:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech1:15\">ZEC 1:15</a></p>",
